{"tid":470710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持香港獨立嘅應該向支那人民輸出革命","createTime":"2017-11-16T14:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T06:30:08.000Z","uid":143241,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"973b2f1f725f5de99e98e1fa6664fa53f6d76431","tid":470710,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"唔好以為大陸發生嘅嘢唔關你事,上面十幾億人有一成人搞事可能就已經推翻咗共產黨！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫繡花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，文質彬彬，那樣溫良恭儉讓。革命是暴動，是一個階級推翻一個階級的暴烈的行動</span></span>"},{"pid":"6e7961418d0c9252eb1d6539a9a3f0534f01d433","tid":470710,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:24:14.000Z","msg":"啱呀，所以彊獨藏獨台獨都應該支持"},{"pid":"4f41fd2a077022deef9373080af875244449881a","tid":470710,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱呀，所以彊獨藏獨台獨都應該支持</blockquote><br />\n台獨就等國民政府返攻咗大陸至算喇"},{"pid":"a72116ba684d4ce2414405c9f9265d54dd759643","tid":470710,"uid":26303,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"推反一個黨，下個黨仲仆街咁點算好啊？"},{"pid":"7924a5b27c5435f7dbff98372f01d7e76a7e07a1","tid":470710,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推反一個黨，下個黨仲仆街咁點算好啊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立呀<br />\n<br />\n乜野「推反一個黨」??<br />\n<br />\n九唔搭八"},{"pid":"5b594f25772a21e8b85461d07b99b20cafbb44c2","tid":470710,"uid":26303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推反一個黨，下個黨仲仆街咁點算好啊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立呀<br />\n<br />\n乜野「推反一個黨」??<br />\n<br />\n九唔搭八</blockquote><br />\n你再睇多次樓主寫咩啊，可能你睇得太快"},{"pid":